description.en: Chuck Solo is a famous junk food smuggler; that’s why he’s called "Ham"
metaDescription.en: Chuck Solo is a famous junk food smuggler; that’s why he’s called "Ham"

description.en: Red Skywalker is a committed Rebel and is learning to be a Jedi Bird warrior.
metaDescription.en: Red Skywalker is a committed Rebel and is learning to be a Jedi Bird warrior.

description.en: Chuck is Red’s loyal friend and the fastest of the Birds. He acts before he thinks and this often lands him in trouble.
metaDescription.en: Chuck is Red’s loyal friend and the fastest of the Birds. He acts before he thinks and this often lands him in trouble.

description.en: C-3PYOLK is a Protocol Droid and interpreter. A Droid of Peace, he is always trying to find diplomatic solutions
metaDescription.en: C-3PYOLK is a Protocol Droid and interpreter. A Droid of Peace, he is always trying to find diplomatic solutions

description.en: Pigtroopers keep looking for junk food around the universe and deliver it to their ruler Emperor Piglatine. They don’t think for themselves, they merely follow orders and often fail in whatever they are trying to do
metaDescription.en: Pigtroopers keep looking for junk food around the universe and deliver it to their ruler Emperor Piglatine. They don’t think for themselves, they merely follow orders and often fail in whatever they are trying to do

description.en:
Looks can fool you: Stella might look like a chick in need of rescuing, but her feisty character is far from a helpless girl!
Now available as a cuddly plush toy in various sizes.
metaDescription.en:
Looks can fool you: Stella might look like a chick in need of rescuing, but her feisty character is far from a helpless girl!

description.en: Once a Jedi Bird warrior, now fighting for the pigs!
metaDescription.en: Once a Jedi Bird warrior, now fighting for the pigs!

description.en: Princess Stella Organa is one of the leaders of the Bird Republic. She’s stubborn, dramatic and expects everybody to obey her and at the same time she wants to destroy the Pig Empire to free the birds’ home planet
metaDescription.en: Princess Stella Organa is one of the leaders of the Bird Republic. She’s stubborn, dramatic and expects everybody to obey her and at the same time she wants to destroy the Pig Empire to free the birds’ home planet

description.en: Obi-Wan Kaboomi is a Jedi Bird warrior and very proud of his powers, although he can’t always control his explosions
metaDescription.en: Obi-Wan Kaboomi is a Jedi Bird warrior and very proud of his powers, although he can’t always control his explosions

description.en: No Angry Birds Star Wars collections is complete without Yoda – the Jedi trainer of Luke Skywalker and Grand Master of the Jedi Council!
metaDescription.en: No Angry Birds Star Wars collections is complete without Yoda – the Jedi trainer of Luke Skywalker and Grand Master of the Jedi Council!

description.en: Corporal pig is the loyal leader of the King’s army. He tirelessly leads his troops from failure to failure.
metaDescription.en: Corporal pig is the loyal leader of the King’s army. He tirelessly leads his troops from failure to failure.

description.en: Terebacca is Ham Solo’s co-pilot and mechanic. Seems to be emotionless and communicates only by grunting and staring
metaDescription.en: Terebacca is Ham Solo’s co-pilot and mechanic. Seems to be emotionless and communicates only by grunting and staring

description.en:
Luke, I’m your… feather, right?
Anyway, this plush toy is a legend.

description.en: Lazer Bird is one of the fastest things in the universe whenever he uses his super power the Ultimate Lazer Rush. Lazer Bird is the joker of the group and being a little impatient he often gets the flock into trouble.

description.en: The Lightning Birds travel in a pack of three. They are adventurers whose curiosity and liveliness drives the birds face new challenges. Their super power, the Triple Vaporizer, comes handy in the freezing hollowness of space.
